<HEADLINE> Brief Summary of Wimbledon Results </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WIMBLEDON, England (AP) -- A brief look at what happened Thursday  
on the fourth day of the Wimbledon tennis championships: 
</P>
<P>
	-- Weather: Cloudy and warm with no rain for the fourth day. High  
temperature was 72F. 
</P>
