	-- Attendance: 40,312, a record for the fourth day. Previous  
record was 39,813 in 1986. Last year on the fourth day it was 
37,423. The total attendance so far is 155,378, an increase of 
14,426 over last year. 
</P>
<P>
	-- Seeded winners -- Men: No. 2 Patrick Rafter, No. 4 Andre  
Agassi, No. 5 Richard Krajicek, No. 6 Tim Henman, No. 8 Todd 
Martin, No. 10 Goran Ivanisevic, No. 11 Gustavo Kuerten, No. 14 
Tommy Haas. 
</P>
