</P>
<P>
	-- Seeded winners -- Women: No. 3 Lindsay Davenport, No. 5 Jana  
Novotna, No. 9 Mary Pierce, No. 11 Julie Halard-Decugis, No. 14 
Barbara Schett. 
</P>
<P>
	Upsets: No. 7 Arantxa Sanchez Vicario by unseeded Lisa Raymond,  
No. 16 Natasha Zvereva by unseeded Tatiana Panova. 
</P>
<P>
	-- Stat of the Day: There were 28 break points as Jelena Dokic  
beat Katarina Studenikova 6-0, 4-6, 8-6. There were 13 breaks of 
serve. 
</P>
<P>
	-- Quote of the Day: ``I can't say this is my place anymore. I  
used to own it, but Pete Sampras has taken over the keys.'' -- Boris 
Becker. 
  	   	
</P>
