public offering Wednesday. GlobeSpan, which makes chips used in 
technology for high-speed Internet access, saw its shares more than 
double from the offering price. 

</P>
<P>
 *SCM Microsystems, down 5 1/2 at 48 7/8    	
</P>
<P>
	SCM will take a charge of about $7 million in the second quarter  
as it plans to acquire a majority stake in Dazzle Multimedia. SCM 
provides hardware and software for data security programs. Dazzle 
makes digital video products. 

</P>
