<HEADLINE> Lennon's 'Walrus' Lyrics To Be Sold </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LONDON (AP) -- Just what was the Walrus trying to say? An  
alternative set of lyrics to John Lennon's enigmatic song ``I Am 
the Walrus'' may help some lucky fan find out. 
</P>
<P>
