<HEADLINE> Wynonna Divorces Her Husband </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	FRANKLIN, Tenn. (AP) -- Wynonna has divorced her husband of three  
years and will pay him $250,000. 
</P>
<P>
	The settlement with Arch Kelley became final on Wednesday.  
</P>
<P>
	The 35-year-old country star will be primarily responsible for  
the couple's two children, ages 3 and 4, who will live with her. 
</P>
<P>
	Wynonna and Kelley, a former yacht salesman, were married in  
1996. She filed for divorce in November, citing irreconcilable 
differences. 
  	   	
