<CATEGORY> international </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> AP Top International Headlines At 3:29 p.m. EDT </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 *U.S. Offers $5M Reward for Justice  
</P>
<P>
 *China Stops Landing of U.S. Plane	
